staxel.village.dialogue.Ren.line:1000050: (안함)Then I suppose I can ask for some help...
staxel.village.dialogue.Ren.line:1000060: (안함)I don't have much time, but I need to get a message through to ^c:1486b0;Leif^c:pop;.
staxel.village.dialogue.Ren.line:1000150: (안함)Sorry, I can't spare the energy to speak.
staxel.village.dialogue.Ren.line:1000160: (안함)I need to conserve fuel for the journey home.
staxel.village.dialogue.Ren.line:1000190: (안함)So what did he say? Will he return with me?
staxel.village.dialogue.Ren.line:1000200: (안함)I can read it in your face... I see...
staxel.village.dialogue.Ren.line:1000220: (안함)We had hoped it wouldn't come to this, but please deliver these to the local ^c:1486b0;scientist^c:pop;.
staxel.village.dialogue.Ren.line:1000230: (안함)I suspect this will change his mind...
